Package: inlaVP
Type: Package
Title: Variance Partitioning disease mapping models
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
  person(given = "Massimo", family = "Ventrucci", email = "massimo.ventrucci@unibo.it", role = c("aut", "cre")),
  person(given = "Maria", family = "Franco-Villoria", email = "maria.francovilloria@unimore.it", role = c("aut")))
Maintainer: Massimo Ventrucci <massimo.ventrucci@unibo.it>
Description: This package contains functions to fit Variance Partiotioning (VP) 
    disease mapping models in R-INLA; the models are described in the paper by Franco-Villoria M, Ventrucci M, Rue H. 
    'Variance partitioning in spatio-temporal disease mapping models'. arXiv:2109.13374
License: GPL
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
Suggests: INLA
Imports: Matrix, numDeriv
LazyData: true
